{{flavour|A staff that increases the power of fire spells cast by its wielder, and protects them from the effects of fire. If the wielder is skilled in Evocations and Fire Magic, they can burn those struck by it, dealing fire damage which bypasses armour.}}

A '''staff of fire''' is a [[magical staff]]. It gives a [[spell enhancer]] to [[Fire Magic]], and gives the wielder a rank of [[fire resistance]].

The staff can also be used in combat, functioning as a +0 [[staff]] that deals additional fire damage:

{{crawlquote|'''Fire Damage''': A random amount ranging from 0 to 1.25×(Evocations/2 + Fire Magic)<br>'''Chance to Activate on a Hit''': (Evocations + Fire Magic/2)×6.66% per hit}}

In addition, the [[Staves]] and [[Fighting]] skills will increase the damage done by the staff itself.

==History==
{{CBA|0.32|the maximum fire damage in melee will be increased to <code>1.575×(Evocations/2 + Fire Magic)</code> and be reduced by AC.}}
*Prior to [[0.19]], enhancer staves would penalize casting spells of the opposite school.
*Prior to [[0.8]], the chance of a staff of fire auto-identifying when wielded depended on the Fire Magic skill of the wielder.
